    "body": "closes #21343 \r\n\r\nThis PR adds a new unit test to check that detection of relevant packages is performed correctly in a few scenarios mocking real use-cases. Data for each package tested is in a YAML file under `$spack/lib/spack/spack/test/data`. This addition is in view of improving the robustness of the detection logic for packages that provide widely used services (compilers, MPIs, etc.)\r\n\r\nModifications:\r\n\r\n- [x] Added a test to check that detection for packages is performed correctly\r\n- [x] Added documentation on how to write detection tests for each package\r\n- [x] Added detection tests for `gcc`, `llvm` and `intel`\r\n- [x] Fixed a bit in our prefix deduction logic that was preventing `intel` from being detected",
    "performed_via_github_app": null
